T02TD1250E:210b-1: shr'i he badzra s'a dha nam /
T02TD1250E:210b-3: dpal kye'i rdo rje'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD1250E:211a-2: dpal ldan dgyes pa'i rdo rje dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-3: sgo bzhir gnas pa'i goo r'i sogs //
T02TD1250E:211a-4: mtshams kyi skul byed ma bzhi la //
T02TD1250E:211a-5: sgo gsum dad pas phyag 'tshal te //
T02TD1250E:211a-6: rnal 'byor blo zhan don du ni //
T02TD1250E:211a-7: bdag gis dgyes pa'i rdo rje yi //
T02TD1250E:211a-8: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sgrub thabs 'di //
T02TD1250E:211a-9: mi nus bzhin du brtsam par bya //
T02TD1250E:211a-10: slob dpon de nyid thos pa dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-11: dbang rnams tshul bzhin mnos pa dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-12: bsgom dang cho ga mkhas pa dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-13: bka' yi gnang ba thob pa yis //
T02TD1250E:211a-14: dngos grub 'dod pa'i sems kyis su //
T02TD1250E:211a-15: dur khrod dang ni lha rten dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-16: rang gi khyim dang chu 'gram du //
T02TD1250E:211a-17: 'jigs pa'i sems med bsam gtan bya //
T02TD1250E:211a-18: dran thar rnam pa bdun dag gis //
T02TD1250E:211a-19: lus sogs bdun po dag nas ni //
T02TD1250E:211a-20: skad cig ma yi rnal 'byor mas //
T02TD1250E:211a-21: rdo rje sems dpa'i lus byas te //
T02TD1250E:211a-23: de steng nyid dkyil h'u% bsam ste //
T02TD1250E:211a-24: 'bar ba me yis rab bsregs pas //
T02TD1250E:211a-25: ye shes mig dang ldan bya ste //
T02TD1250E:211a-26: sngon du dgyes pa'i rdo rje dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-27: lha mo brgyad dag mngon par mthong //
T02TD1250E:211a-28: phyi dang nang dang bla med pa'i //
T02TD1250E:211a-29: mchod pa rnams kyis yang dag mchod //
T02TD1250E:211a-30: sngon 'gro rjes su phyag byas te //
T02TD1250E:211a-31: sdig pa byas pa bshags pa dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-32: phyis mi byed par sdom pa gzung //
T02TD1250E:211a-33: dge ba byas byed yi rang bya //
T02TD1250E:211a-34: sangs rgyas dgyes pa'i rdo rje dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-35: de gsungs pa yi chos rnams dang //
T02TD1250E:211a-36: ma brgyad lha mo dge 'dun la //
T02TD1250E:211a-37: bdag ni dang bas skyabs su mchi //
T02TD1250E:211a-38: byang chub sems kyang bdag gis bskyed //
T02TD1250E:211a-39: theg pa chen po la gnas bgyi //
T02TD1250E:211a-40: kun gyi don ni bdag nyid dbul //
T02TD1250E:211a-41: de yang rgya cher bsngo bar bgyi //
T02TD1250E:211a-42: dang po byams pa bsgom par bya //
T02TD1250E:211a-43: gnyis pa snying rje bye brag bsgom //
T02TD1250E:211a-44: gsum pa dga' ba bsgom pa ste //
T02TD1250E:211a-45: kun gyi tha mar btang snyoms so //
T02TD1250E:211a-46: dang po stong pa'i byang chub sems //
T02TD1250E:211a-47: gnyis pa la ni sa bon 'dus //
T02TD1250E:211a-48: gsum pa la ni gzugs rdzogs te //
T02TD1250E:211a-49: bzhi pa la ni yig 'bru dgod //
T02TD1250E:211a-50: de 'og stong pa'i byang chub ni //
T02TD1250E:211a-51: phyi dang nang med stong smin no //
T02TD1250E:211a-52: bsams nas de nyid kho na yi //
T02TD1250E:211b-0: lus su yang dag @211b bsgom par bya //
T02TD1250E:211b-1: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dznya' na badzra sa bh'a ba a'a tma ko& ham /
T02TD1250E:211b-2: sngon gyi smon lam rjes dran na //
T02TD1250E:211b-3: de kho na nyid las langs nas //
T02TD1250E:211b-5: de steng nyi ma h'u% bsams pas //
T02TD1250E:211b-6: h'u% las rdo rje'i sa gzhir gyur //
T02TD1250E:211b-7: de steng bgegs skrad h'u% bsams pa'i //
T02TD1250E:211b-8: raksha sgra dang ldan pa yis //
T02TD1250E:211b-9: tshogs kyi bgegs rnams sel bar byed //
T02TD1250E:211b-10: slar 'dus rdo rje'i gur du gyur //
T02TD1250E:211b-11: bla re yang ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1250E:211b-12: steng 'og phyogs med rdo rje'i dbyings //
T02TD1250E:211b-13: sgo yi dbyibs 'dra nyid du bsgom //
T02TD1250E:211b-14: ae gzugs bdag med ma 'dra bar //
T02TD1250E:211b-16: chos kyi 'byung gnas de dbyibs ni //
T02TD1250E:211b-17: gru gsum gyen dkar yang dag ldan //
T02TD1250E:211b-18: de yi dbus su bsam pa ni //
T02TD1250E:211b-19: ya% dang ra% dang ba% dang la% //
T02TD1250E:211b-20: de steng bdag nyid rnam shes ni //
T02TD1250E:211b-21: ao% ba% nyid ni yang dag gnas //
T02TD1250E:211b-22: spro dang bsdu ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1250E:211b-23: gzhal yas khang du gyur pa ste //
T02TD1250E:211b-24: thog gcig pa ru bsam par bya //
T02TD1250E:211b-25: ngos bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD1250E:211b-26: ka ba brgyad dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD1250E:211b-27: rta babs bzhis kyang rnam par mdzes //
T02TD1250E:211b-28: dra ba dra phyed kyis brgyan pa //
T02TD1250E:211b-29: lha mo brgyad kyi 'od kyis kyang //
T02TD1250E:211b-30: gsal bar lha yi rnam par byas //
T02TD1250E:211b-32: / kha dog dmar po nyi ma gnas //
T02TD1250E:211b-33: de steng bdud bzhi rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1250E:211b-34: tshangs pa dbang po nye dbang drag //
T02TD1250E:211b-35: shar sgo la sogs bzhir gnas pa //
T02TD1250E:211b-36: tshangs pa dang ni dbang po dang //
T02TD1250E:211b-37: nye dbang dang ni drag po ste //
T02TD1250E:211b-38: rim pa bzhin du gnas pa'o //
T02TD1250E:211b-39: mtshams bzhi por ni shes bya ba //
T02TD1250E:211b-40: gshin rje dang ni nor bdag dang //
T02TD1250E:211b-41: bden bral dang ni thags bzangs ris //
T02TD1250E:211b-42: pukka s'i sogs gdan du brtag / de ltar pho brang bye brag rdzogs //
T02TD1250E:211b-43: de bzhin gshegs pa 'byung ba yi //
T02TD1250E:211b-44: nga rgyal 'di yis bya ba ste //
T02TD1250E:211b-45: nga 'am bdag tu bsam par bya //
T02TD1250E:211b-46: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta badzra sva bh'a ba a'a tma kom& ham /
T02TD1250E:211b-47: dbus kyi gzhi steng a'a li ni //
T02TD1250E:211b-48: bcu drug rim pa gnyis shes bya //
T02TD1250E:211b-49: de 'gyur zla ba gnyis pa ni //
T02TD1250E:211b-50: me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
T02TD1250E:211b-51: de steng yang dag bsam pa ni //
T02TD1250E:211b-52: k'a li bzhi bcu nyis 'gyur las //
T02TD1250E:211b-53: rta bdun pa ru gyur pa ste //
T02TD1250E:211b-54: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
T02TD1250E:212a-1: dbus h'u% las byung ba ni //
T02TD1250E:212a-2: rdo rje nag po rtse lnga pa //
T02TD1250E:212a-3: lte ba h'u% gis mtshan pa ste //
T02TD1250E:212a-4: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
T02TD1250E:212a-6: byas te bzhi po nyid la bstim //
T02TD1250E:212a-7: 'od kyi gong bur gyur pa ni //
T02TD1250E:212a-8: bya ba nan tan ye shes so //
T02TD1250E:212a-9: de las thig le brgyad chad de //
T02TD1250E:212a-10: ga% dang tsa% dang ba% dang gha% //
T02TD1250E:212a-11: pa% dang sa% dang la% dang da% //
T02TD1250E:212a-12: zla ba nyi ma yang dag ldan //
T02TD1250E:212a-13: sa bon brgyad las gyur pa ni //
T02TD1250E:212a-14: gri dang rde'u chung rus sbal sbrul //
T02TD1250E:212a-15: seng ge dge slong 'khor lo dang //
T02TD1250E:212a-16: rdo rje la sogs rim par skyes //
T02TD1250E:212a-17: goo r'i shar gyi sgo na gnas //
T02TD1250E:212a-18: tsoo r'i lto yi sgo na gnas //
T02TD1250E:212a-19: nub kyi sgo ru be tt'a l'i //
T02TD1250E:212a-20: byang gi sgo ru gha sma r'i //
T02TD1250E:212a-21: pukka s'i ni dbang ldan du //
T02TD1250E:212a-22: ri khrod ma ni byin za'i grvar //
T02TD1250E:212a-23: gtum mo bden bral la gnas te //
T02TD1250E:212a-24: g-yung mo 'di ru rlung na gnas //
T02TD1250E:212a-25: lha mo bskyed pa rdzogs nas su //
T02TD1250E:212a-26: gtso bo 'od kyi gong bu la //
T02TD1250E:212a-27: lha mos bdag po med mthong nas //
T02TD1250E:212a-28: gong bu mchog la gsol pa gdab //
T02TD1250E:212a-29: snying rje yid kyis bcom ldan bzhengs //
T02TD1250E:212a-30: pukka s'i ni bdag la skyobs //
T02TD1250E:212a-31: stong pa'i ting 'dzin spangs nas ni //
T02TD1250E:212a-32: bdag la 'dod pa'i bde ba mdzod //
T02TD1250E:212a-33: khyod mi bzhugs na bdag 'gum pas //
T02TD1250E:212a-34: stong pa'i rang bzhin yangs spangs te //
T02TD1250E:212a-35: ri khrod ma 'bras grub par ni //
T02TD1250E:212a-36: kye yi rdo rje khyod bzhengs shig /'jig rten phyir smon 'dod pa'i gtso //
T02TD1250E:212a-37: ci phyir stong pa nyid la bzhugs //
T02TD1250E:212a-38: khyod mi bzhugs na phyogs mi khums //
T02TD1250E:212a-39: gtum mo bdag ni gsol ba 'debs //
T02TD1250E:212a-40: g-yung mo bdag ni yid rmongs pas //
T02TD1250E:212a-41: snying rje rgyun chad ma mdzad par //
T02TD1250E:212a-42: khyod kyi bdag ni thugs 'tshal kyis //
T02TD1250E:212a-43: mig 'phrul lta bur khyod bzhengs shig / bskul ba'i glu'o //
T02TD1250E:212a-44: bskul bas sngon gyi byang chub ni //
T02TD1250E:212a-45: smon lam rjes su dran te bzhengs //
T02TD1250E:212a-46: zhal gcig phyag gnyis nag po chen //
T02TD1250E:212a-47: gcer bu spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1250E:212a-48: phyag rgya lnga dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD1250E:212a-49: sna tshogs rdo rje spyi bor gnas //
T02TD1250E:212a-50: g-yas na rdo rje rtse lnga 'dzin //
T02TD1250E:212a-51: g-yon pa na ni thod pa 'dzin //
T02TD1250E:212a-52: zhabs kyis bdud bzhi rnam par mnan //
T02TD1250E:212a-53: brkyang bskum tshul du gnas pa'o //
T02TD1250E:212a-54: goo r'i kha dog nag mo ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-0: tsoo @212b r'i kha dog btsod dang mtshungs //
T02TD1250E:212b-1: ro langs ma ni gser bsregs mdog / za phod ma ni margat mtshungs //
T02TD1250E:212b-2: sbos mo'i mdog ni sngon mo'o //
T02TD1250E:212b-3: ri khrod ma ni zla nor 'od //
T02TD1250E:212b-4: gtum mo nam mkha' ljang gu ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-5: g-yung mo sna tshogs pa ru 'dod //
T02TD1250E:212b-6: goo r'i g-yas na gri gug ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-7: g-yon na nya ni de bzhin no //
T02TD1250E:212b-8: chom rkun g-yas na da ma ru //
T02TD1250E:212b-9: g-yon pa na ni phag pa'o //
T02TD1250E:212b-10: ro langs g-yas na rus sbal te //
T02TD1250E:212b-11: g-yon pa na ni padma'i snod //
T02TD1250E:212b-12: za phod ma yi g-yas na sbrul //
T02TD1250E:212b-13: g-yon pa'i lag na thod pa'o //
T02TD1250E:212b-14: sbos mo g-yas na seng ge ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-15: g-yon gyi phyag na dgra sta 'dzin //
T02TD1250E:212b-16: rngon pa ma g-yas dge slong ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-17: g-yon pa na ni gsil byed do //
T02TD1250E:212b-18: gtum mo g-yas na 'khor lo ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-19: g-yon pa na ni thod pa 'dzin //
T02TD1250E:212b-20: g-yung mo g-yas na rdo rje ste //
T02TD1250E:212b-21: g-yon na sdigs mdzub de bzhin no //
T02TD1250E:212b-22: skyil krung phyed pa'i gar gyis gnas //
T02TD1250E:212b-23: goo r'i la sogs phyag gnyis shes //
T02TD1250E:212b-24: spyan gsum sgra ni gyen du yin //
T02TD1250E:212b-25: phyag rgya lngas ni shin tu mdzes //
T02TD1250E:212b-26: tshangs pa la sogs gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD1250E:212b-27: de ltar sku rnams rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD1250E:212b-28: rang gi snying gar padma bsam //
T02TD1250E:212b-29: de dbus nyi ma h'um las bsam //
T02TD1250E:212b-30: de las rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
T02TD1250E:212b-31: de las h'u% gis mtshan pa ste ;
T02TD1250E:212b-32: / de 'gyur ye shes sems dpa' bsam //
T02TD1250E:212b-33: de nyid pad nyir h'u% rdo rje //
T02TD1250E:212b-34: ye shes sems dpa' rdzogs pa'o //
T02TD1250E:212b-35: de ltar rim pa kun la yang //
T02TD1250E:212b-36: de ltar nang du shes par bya //
T02TD1250E:212b-38: dza: h'u% ba ho: bka' lung gis //
T02TD1250E:212b-39: goo r'i la sogs rnams kyis ni //
T02TD1250E:212b-40: spyan drangs nas ni de bstims nas //
T02TD1250E:212b-42: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' ni //
T02TD1250E:212b-43: bsgrubs te gzhan na yod ma yin / ma% las gti mug rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:212b-44: da% las zhe sdang rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:212b-45: ma% las ser sna rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:212b-46: ra% las 'dod chags rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:212b-47: aa% las phrag dog rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:212b-48: na% las bdag med rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:212b-49: mig dang rna ba sna dang lce //
T02TD1250E:212b-50: lus yid rim bzhin de ltar dgod //
T02TD1250E:212b-51: phyag gnyis zhal gcig ro yi gdan //
T02TD1250E:212b-52: gri gug thod pa phyag na bsnams //
T02TD1250E:212b-53: ao% las mkha' spyod mar shes bya //
T02TD1250E:213a-2: h'u% las zhabs bskyed 'og nas bsam //
T02TD1250E:213a-3: de ltar sku gsung thugs de yang //
T02TD1250E:213a-5: rang snying sa bo khyad par spro //
T02TD1250E:213a-6: lcags kyu'i gzugs kyi 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1250E:213a-7: sangs rgyas spyan drangs mdun du mchod//
T02TD1250E:213a-8: dbang bskur ba ni blang ba ste //
T02TD1250E:213a-9: mgon po de bzhin gshegs thams cad //
T02TD1250E:213a-10: khyod kyis bdag la dbang bskur cig / de bzhin gshegs pa khro bo dang //
T02TD1250E:213a-11: lha rnams kyis ni mdun bdar nas //
T02TD1250E:213a-12: bum pas de la dbang bskur bas //
T02TD1250E:213a-16: bi la / skad cig bzhi la'o //
T02TD1250E:213a-18: pa ra m'a nan da dang //
T02TD1250E:213a-19: bi ra m'a nan da dang /
T02TD1250E:213a-28: bde ba chen po'i de kho na nyid do //
T02TD1250E:213a-29: mtha' ru dbang rnams 'bras bu ni //
T02TD1250E:213a-30: rtsa bar mi bskyod pas brgyan pa'o //
T02TD1250E:213a-31: sems dang phan pa rin chen dang //
T02TD1250E:213a-33: goo r'i tsoo r'i bett'a l'i //
T02TD1250E:213a-34: gha sma r'i rnams brgyan pa'o //
T02TD1250E:213a-35: mi bskyod sangs rgyas rin chen dang //
T02TD1250E:213a-36: tshe dpag med kyis brgyan pa ni //
T02TD1250E:213a-37: sbos mo rngon ma gtum mo dang //
T02TD1250E:213a-38: g-yung mo la sogs brgyad pa'o //
T02TD1250E:213a-39: aom aa bhi shi nytsa tu m'am sarba ta th'a ga ta ho //
T02TD1250E:213a-42: de 'gyur bdud rtsi ro myang ba //
T02TD1250E:213a-43: rdo rje nas kyi 'bru bsam ste //
T02TD1250E:213a-44: dgyes pa'i rdo rje de bklag go //
T02TD1250E:213a-45: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta aa mri ta sva da na badzra sva bh'a ba a'a tma ko& ham /
T02TD1250E:213a-46: lha mo brgyad rnams spros nas ni //
T02TD1250E:213a-47: mchod pa brgyad kyis sngon bzhin du //
T02TD1250E:213a-48: skyil 'khor gtso bo nyid la mchod //
T02TD1250E:213a-49: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta p'u dza badzra sva bh'a ba a'a tma ko& ham //
T02TD1250E:213a-50: rnal 'byor ma rnams de dag gis //
T02TD1250E:213a-51: 'khor lo'i gtso bo la bstod la //
T02TD1250E:213a-52: khyod ni rnal 'byor brgyad kyis bskor //
T02TD1250E:213a-53: nyid kyi thugs kyi khyod dgongs 'grub //
T02TD1250E:213a-54: rgyu dang mi rgyu 'khor ba kun 'grub pa //
T02TD1250E:213a-55: snying rje'i thugs kyis sems can byang chub tu //
T02TD1250E:213a-56: kun rdzob sgyu mas sgrub pa'i yid dgyes mdzod //
T02TD1250E:213a-57: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta stu tir badzra sva bh'a ba a'a tma ko& ham //
T02TD1250E:213a-58: de yan chad bsnyen pa dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa bshad nas //
T02TD1250E:213b-0: @213b sgrub pa dang sgrub pa chen po bshad par bya ste //
T02TD1250E:213b-1: dkyil 'khor lha rnams lus la bsdu //
T02TD1250E:213b-2: lte bar tsa nda l'i sbar la //
T02TD1250E:213b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga bsregs te //
T02TD1250E:213b-4: spyan la sogs pa yang bsregs te //
T02TD1250E:213b-5: bsregs pas ham las ri bong 'byung //
T02TD1250E:213b-6: dang po sprin dang 'dra ba mthong //
T02TD1250E:213b-7: gnyis su du ba 'dra ba mthong //
T02TD1250E:213b-8: gsum pa glog gi rnam pa ste //
T02TD1250E:213b-9: bzhi pa mar me 'dra ba dang //
T02TD1250E:213b-10: lnga pa thams cad snang ba ste //
T02TD1250E:213b-11: sprin med nam mkha' 'dra ba ste //
T02TD1250E:213b-12: phyis ni sgyu ma'i rnam pa mtshungs //
T02TD1250E:213b-13: rmi lam rnam pa skad cig go //
T02TD1250E:213b-14: rang gi snying ga 'di nyid du //
T02TD1250E:213b-15: spros dang bsdu ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1250E:213b-16: spros med bsgom pa'i sbyor ba ste //
T02TD1250E:213b-17: thog ma mtha' dbus med pa yi //
T02TD1250E:213b-19: de ltar ma yin dmigs ma yin //
T02TD1250E:213b-20: zhes mar me'i rtse mo'i bar du'o //
T02TD1250E:213b-21: bar chod bgegs kyis mi tshugs phyir //
T02TD1250E:213b-22: gtor ma rgyun tu sbyin par bya /
T02TD1250E:213b-23: aom ainda dza ma dza la /
T02TD1250E:213b-41: kha nti khu ni phe da g'a da /
T02TD1250E:213b-42: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dha rm'a n'um /
T02TD1250E:213b-43: a'a dya nu tpa nna tv'a ta /
T02TD1250E:213b-44: aom a'a: h'u% phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1250E:213b-45: aom tree lo ky'a kshe pa h'u% h'u% h'u% phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1250E:213b-47: bsam gtan mi nus rnal 'byor gang //
T02TD1250E:213b-48: de ni dag pa rjes su dran //
T02TD1250E:213b-49: snying rje'i spyan ni dmar po ste //
T02TD1250E:213b-50: yan lag nag po byams pa yin //
T02TD1250E:213b-51: phyag rgya lnga ni sangs rgyas yin //
T02TD1250E:213b-52: khros pas gdug pa 'dul ba yin //
T02TD1250E:213b-53: spyan gsum pa ni sku gsum mo //
T02TD1250E:213b-54: rus pa bden pa bzhi po'o //
T02TD1250E:213b-55: gzugs kyi phung po rdo rje me //
T02TD1250E:213b-56: tshor ba gsang ba'i goo r'i ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-59: rnam par shes pa bdag med ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-60: don dam la ni phung po med //
T02TD1250E:213b-61: skye mched drug ni dag pa ni /
T02TD1250E:213b-62: mig ni gti mug rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-63: rna ba zhe sdang rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-64: sna la ser sna rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-65: kha la 'dod chags rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-66: lus la phrag dog rdo rje ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-67: sa ni pukka s'i ru bshad //
T02TD1250E:213b-68: chu yi khams ni rngon pa ma //
T02TD1250E:213b-69: drod ni gtum mor shes par bya //
T02TD1250E:213b-70: rlung ni g-yung mor rab tu grags //
T02TD1250E:214a-0: gzugs ni goo r'ir ra yang @214a * //
T02TD1250E:214a-2: sgra ni chom rkun ma rab brjod //
T02TD1250E:214a-3: dri ni ro langs ma ru bshad //
T02TD1250E:214a-4: ro yi tshul ni za phod ma //
T02TD1250E:214a-5: reg bya sa spyod ma zhes bya //
T02TD1250E:214a-6: chos kyi dbyings ni mkha' spyod ma //
T02TD1250E:214a-7: de ltar dag pas rjes dran bya //
T02TD1250E:214a-8: bdag gi sgrub thabs rim pa 'di //
T02TD1250E:214a-9: blo zhan don du bdag gis brtsams //
T02TD1250E:214a-10: de yi dge ba gang yin pas //
T02TD1250E:214a-11: sems can 'khor ba las grol shog / dpal dgyes pa rdo rje'i sgrub thabs //
T02TD1250E:214a-12: slob dpon chen po bde ba'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1250E:214a-14: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dharma tsandra dang /
T02TD1250E:214a-15: lo ts'a ba dharma tsandras rang 'gyur du bsgyur zhing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o /
T02TD1250E:214a-17: // / zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
